        </div>
        <p class="section-lede">Helix is built by Questeria (Anthony DeMarco). Reach him at <a href="mailto:ajdemarco10@gmail.com" style="color: var(--violet); text-decoration: underline;">ajdemarco10@gmail.com</a> or on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/anthony-demarco10/" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--violet); text-decoration: underline;">LinkedIn</a> — all routes are on the <a href="/contact/" style="color: var(--violet); text-decoration: underline;">contact page</a>.</p>
