      <span class="eyebrow">Don't take our word for it</span>
      <h2>The whole point is that you can check.</h2>
      <p>One committed command rebuilds the compiler from 299 hand-authored bytes and proves the fixpoint. The verified model runs are gated against an independent oracle. Start anywhere.</p>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/verify/">See the verified run <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
